Package: hefesto-dualsense4unix
Version: 3.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
         gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1, libhidapi-hidraw0,
         python3-pydantic, python3-structlog, python3-typer,
         python3-platformdirs, python3-rich, python3-evdev, python3-xlib,
         python3-filelock
Recommends: python3-uinput
Maintainer: Hefesto - Dualsense4Unix Project <noreply@example.com>
Description: Daemon Linux para gatilhos adaptativos do controle DualSense
 Hefesto - Dualsense4Unix e um daemon user-level que habilita os gatilhos
 adaptativos do DualSense (Sony) em Linux, com suporte a perfis automaticos
 por janela ativa, lightbar RGB, rumble, emulacao Xbox 360 via uinput,
 e GUI GTK3 com 10 abas (Status, Gatilhos, Lightbar, Rumble, Perfis,
 Daemon, Emulacao, Mouse, Teclado, Firmware).
 .
 Dependencias Python nao empacotadas no Debian (pydualsense, python-uinput)
 devem ser instaladas separadamente via pip:
   pip install pydualsense python-uinput
 .
 Em Ubuntu 22.04 (Jammy) e 24.04 (Noble) o python3-pydantic do apt
 e versao 1.x; o Hefesto - Dualsense4Unix usa API v2. Instale v2 via pip:
   pip install --user 'pydantic>=2'
 Em Ubuntu 25.04 (Plucky) ou derivadas com python3-pydantic 2.x
 no apt, nenhuma acao adicional e necessaria. Runtime imprime aviso
 via warnings.warn se pydantic 1.x for detectado.
 .
 Apos instalacao, habilite o daemon com:
   systemctl --user enable --now hefesto-dualsense4unix.service
